notes:

0. total: neuf
1. source code is written in perl
2. comments are written in english
3. cgi scripts are webpage generating programs invoked by server software that operate according to the cgi specification
4. user access is stored in the database CURRENCY, USERS table, column ADMIN
5. access control bit mask definition is available in the __DATA__ section of DBH.pm and here in user access section
6. database connexion codes are hidden in /var/www/.db 
7. session expiration time is declared constant in DBH.pm
8. a superuser is defined as an user with a first access bit (ADM) enabled
9. counterfeits are not available for users with a last access bit (FOX) disabled


superuser actions:

1. create new user
2. modify user access
3. modify user password
4. delete user


